 href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%93n-m%E1%BB%99t-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-SRRiozBXdTgoMjD9J-OKbA">Tồn một khẩu hào kỳ 1 - 存歿口號其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Tr%C6%B0ng-binh-gia-quy%E1%BA%BFn/poem-TAtZ40jvYoshD-uwy-EmjQ">Trưng binh gia quyến - 徵兵家眷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/Tu%C3%BD-ti%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%A1n-Ph%C3%B2ng-s%E1%BB%A9-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%C3%A2n-Nh%E1%BA%A5t-lai-kinh/poem-jLj6EXJ56Eg9jTfLJQekJg">Tuý tiễn Sơn Phòng sứ Nguyễn Tuân Nhất lai kinh - 醉餞山防使阮遵壹來京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-YRtbQ4Y_EBSiaNimbo26Cg">Lê Khắc Cẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
